sql:
SELECT ensembl_gene_id
FROM genomic_entries
WHERE is_active = 1 AND transcript_status_id = 0;

SELECT biotype_name
FROM biotypes
WHERE is_active = 1;

SELECT biotype_name
FROM biotypes
WHERE biotype_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- well-established biotypes: biotypes with more than 5 entries; 
- bustling biotypes: active biotypes (is_active = 1); 
- fully mapped: transcript status is 'KNOWN';
- blueprint sizes: average lengths of the coding sequence (CDS) and protein sequence.

sql:
SELECT hgnc_name
FROM hgnc
WHERE hgnc_id = '0' AND is_active = 1;

SELECT entrez_name
FROM entrez
WHERE is_active = 1 AND source_database = 'Ensembl';
